  <data name="lblCustomTip.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>&lt;b&gt;Tip:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;br /&gt;
1. Type one or more email addresses (comma separated) &lt;br /&gt;
2. You can also use field tokens provided is required field and validation type is text-&gt;email.&lt;br /&gt;</value>
